{"tid":2098419,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"7月1日起中共嚴控6類人取得外國籍或綠卡","createTime":"2020-07-07T12:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T13:13:12.000Z","uid":346701,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f681fd33bc8dabe4cd0d7fd047480d17ada2d028","tid":2098419,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T12:55:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/07/07/a102887692.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F07%2F07%2Fa102887692.html&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivdToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=8b08b430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/07/07/a102887692.html</a><br />\n<br />\n唔比支國人民去西方文明國家購物,重擊西方國家經濟,<br />\n再啟動經濟內循環、永動機，如果屬實中國將會是最大赢家"},{"pid":"bf5d745bbb15bfb189bedd6f49acfc47d8344706","tid":2098419,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f681fd33bc8dabe4cd0d7fd047480d17ada2d028","tid":2098419,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T12:55:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/07/07/a102887692.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F07%2F07%2Fa102887692.html&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivdToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=8b08b430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/07/07/a102887692.html</a><br />\n<br />\n唔比支國人民去西方文明國家購物,重擊西方國家經濟,<br />\n再啟動經濟內循環、永動機，如果屬實中國將會是最大赢家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T12:56:07.000Z","msg":"【新唐人北京時間2020年07月07日訊】中共《公職人員政務處分法》從7月1日開始正式生效，中國6類在職公職人員持有國外永居證、外國國籍將受到記過或撤職開除等不同程度的處分。有網民認為，這只是給老百姓制定的法規，對權貴階層絲毫不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n中共《公職人員政務處分法》規定：違反規定出境或者辦理因私出境證件的，予以記過或者記大過；情節嚴重的，予以降級或者撤職；違反規定取得外國國籍或者獲取境外永久居留資格、長期居留許可的，予以撤職或者開除。<br />\n<br />\n據中共紀檢委解釋，公職人員包括以下6類人員：<br />\n<br />\n1、公務員以及參照公務員法管理的人員;<br />\n<br />\n2、法律、法規授權或者受國家機關依法委託管理公共事務的組織中從事公務的人員;<br />\n<br />\n3、國有企業管理人員;<br />\n<br />\n4、公辦的教育、科研、文化、醫療衛生、體育等單位中從事管理的人員;<br />\n<br />\n5、基層群眾性自治組織中從事管理的人員;<br />\n<br />\n6、其它依法履行公職的人員。"},{"pid":"0d5bae4e37e18fc8fd8f2f94361a145fbdd2c76b","tid":2098419,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T12:56:56.000Z","msg":"新唐人，法輪功 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b3ba5335b8354aeb3d39feea5cde3cea04581f","tid":2098419,"uid":58630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T12:59:40.000Z","msg":"咁親人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該要加埋入去 愛國就要全家愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa3622e8e0855bd94f4549cbbb1c75c6fb6a428","tid":2098419,"uid":49456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:01:45.000Z","msg":"好快到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a1696a63f311f4878b89a0bde675a52bde8e47","tid":2098419,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:03:11.000Z","msg":"公務員以及參照公務員法管理的人員;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港班狗官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05df6e907e5b81ee2100409f35a01af128250c55","tid":2098419,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"加埋公務員家屬入去啦"},{"pid":"d3b7b9cbe482caadfb8ac2d36baf4127b36a19db","tid":2098419,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:05:41.000Z","msg":"香港理應跟隨"},{"pid":"3760b7c3b1ecf1f5053eac3aeb76a4c2d29e80a6","tid":2098419,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8321aba535c08b78488d40975e23f5a3d1280a","tid":2098419,"uid":63782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:13:05.000Z","msg":"又話香港係中共黨員<br />\n幾時到香港公墓員跟隊？"},{"pid":"666ecd3f9777a3797bf7704d891d8cc9b70a6d1f","tid":2098419,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:13:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n中共《公職人員政務處分法》規定：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>違反規定出境</strong></span></span>或者辦理因私出境證件的，予以記過或者記大過；情節嚴重的，予以降級或者撤職；違反規定取得外國國籍或者獲取境外永久居留資格、長期居留許可的，予以撤職或者開除。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>據中共紀檢委解釋，公職人員包括以下6類人員：</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1、公務員以及參照公務員法管理的人員;<br />\n<br />\n2、法律、法規授權或者受國家機關依法委託管理公共事務的組織中從事公務的人員;<br />\n<br />\n3、國有企業管理人員;<br />\n<br />\n4、公辦的教育、科研、文化、醫療衛生、體育等單位中從事管理的人員;<br />\n<br />\n5、基層群眾性自治組織中從事管理的人員;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><br />\n6、其它依法履行公職的人員。</strong></span></span></blockquote><br />\n即係可以包括埋香港嘅公職人員啊?咁唔怪得有位律政司司長搞到要經北京先由倫敦返香港啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}